{"tid":2161483,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點解市民如我地屌販民就係分化","createTime":"2020-08-17T14:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T14:40:56.000Z","uid":216008,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7de93ad22c8eaf52b5a0c530fa2d6f46fea08411","tid":2161483,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:33:04.000Z","msg":"你要留要辭 最緊要係投票<br />\n講緊公投去定你去留<br />\n你地明明叫泛民 點解會由泛民主 變左販售民主<br />\n點解一個公投都唔撚肯搞 仲要出嚟講到自己唔留香港就無得救咁<br />\n而我都想屌柒嗰班話我地分化既泛民打手<br />\n屌你老母 而家市民有意見係咪唔撚比講<br />\n邊個違反民主在先? 邊個唔顧民意在先<br />\n各有乜撚野各做? 即係繼續入個擺撚到明唔係set比你玩既遊戲之後「篤眼篤鼻」就係各有各做<br />\n分化?批鬥? 你地係咪奴化得太緊要 唔記得乜撚野係意見"},{"pid":"6e768f883883e1b33f9422b245af732a43d1a9e9","tid":2161483,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b81343e0ea42c9e75c69b2d63390b3c5794c624","tid":2161483,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e768f883883e1b33f9422b245af732a43d1a9e9","tid":2161483,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:36:38.000Z","msg":"好撚把火"},{"pid":"dff0fb2a836e66a9980e31bb4c75cb0c40cf1f05","tid":2161483,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:38:57.000Z","msg":"陳志全、朱凱迪，請即先行辭職明志，帶領飯民總辭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2161436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2161436</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"73ec155b08ec64de2523a579f662894bd61570fb","tid":2161483,"uid":216008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dff0fb2a836e66a9980e31bb4c75cb0c40cf1f05","tid":2161483,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T14:38:57.000Z","msg":"陳志全、朱凱迪，請即先行辭職明志，帶領飯民總辭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2161436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2161436</a